pn|,,,|st||SK|S|md|1SKQT763H987DACKQ3,SJ852HAKQDJ954C92,SA94H653DT732CA86,HJT42DKQ86CJT754|sv|E|rh||AH|SAFETY PLAYS BOARD 3|NT|^B@2
